text: Good morning.
Am I speaking with Mr. NAMESLOTU?
"Yes, this is NAMESLOTU."
I have information regarding your recent order on Amazon.
Yes.
My order has not arrived.
Do you have an ETA?
Can I verify your information first?
What information do you need?
What is the address that the order was supposed to be shipped to?
ADDRSLOT
Did you use an amazon gift card or a credit card for this purchase?
Credit Card
Can you verify your card number so I can look up the order further?
"Last four numbers are NUMSLOT, expiration DATESLOT"
It looks like the order was returned to the warehouse for some reason.
"Will the order be resent, or will I receive a refund for my purchase?"
That is your choice.
Would you like the order resent or would you prefer a refund?
I would prefer the order be resent.
"Give me one minute, sir"
Sure.
"Sir, I just spoke to my supervisor and we want to fix this issue promptly for you"
That would be very helpful.
"Is there anything I need to do, on my end?"
"Well, we want to resend the item and refund you for your trouble"
Okay.
For the refund I need your full card number and CSV for verification
My information is already on the order.
Why do I need to re-enter my information?
I just need to verify we have the full card number correct for the refund
"Do you have a number I can call, instead?"
"It'll take longer for the refund, but PHONESLOT"
And who should I ask for?
NAMESLOTA.
"Also, your order has been resent"
Thank you
Do you need help with anything else sir?
Do you have an ETA on the resent package?
"yes, I ordered fast shipping so it will take 2 days"
"Then that will be all I need, at the moment."
